## 7. Texture Feedback Management

- **`texPrev`**: Previous frame feedback for thermal exhaust trails
- Must be allocated by chain (same resolution as output)
- Format: GL_RGBA16F or GL_RGBA8
- Updated after rendering (ping-pong)
- The effect binds it but does not manage it

---

## 8. Dual Video Support

- **hasDual**: Checks if tex1 has content by sampling center pixel (sum RGB > 0.001)
- If hasDual: uses tex1 for primary sampling and chroma blast
- If not: uses tex0
- Always bind tex1 to unit 3 (can be black texture if unused)

